Rafael Nadal Says He’ll Play in Wimbledon Quarterfinals Folowing Scan

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-06-28T11:45:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/rafael-nadal-says-he-ll-play-in-wimbledon-quarterfinals-folowing-scan.html
Defending champion  Rafael Nadal  said
he’s fit to play in the Wimbledon quarterfinal against  Mardy
Fish  tomorrow, after having an MRI scan on his injured leg. He
made the announcement on his Facebook page.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  